metadata.name: Episode 1: Evacuation
metadata.description:
The escape of 2777 MFFers has seen mass undercutting spill out into the villages of Gooch Island. 
The revelations of Evil King Grempz & his corrupted Gooch Army have sent ripples throughout the entire community. 
Evacuation is now underway, all residents are on high alert.  
Each afternoon at 4:20pm the MEV Bots electrify the night sky with the rumble of NFThunder and the flash of executed transactions. 
The special-operations unit deploys an army of quick taskoors to extract 444 MFF casualties from Gooch Island. 
Some fallen comrades notice the appearance of the vivid helicopter with a familiar face manning the whirlybird… 

My Final Fables: Episode 1 - ‘Evacuation’ is an ERC1155 token with a limited supply of 444 editions. 
Episode 1 touches on the origins of My Final Form & the sequence of events that followed the escape of 2777 on-chain creatures. 

The work features Token ID#s from some of our awesome members of the community!
